      </div>
      
      <!-- METALS & MATERIALS -->
      <h2>Metals &amp; Materials</h2>
      <div class="container">
        <div class="label">
          <p>Is your jewelry nickel-free?</p>
		</div>
        <hr>
        <div class="content">
          <p>Yes! All of our jewelry is nickel-free.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="container">
        <div class="label">
          <p>What metals are used to make your jewelry?</p>
		</div>
        <hr>
        <div class="content">
          <p>We use 14K gold filled, 925 sterling silver, and 14k solid gold metals to make our 
            pieces. All metals are sourced from Canadian and US manufacturers, with a focus on 
            recycled metal whenever possible.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="container">
        <div class="label">
          <p>What is 14K gold filled?</p>
		</div>
        <hr>
        <div class="content">
          <p>Gold filled metals are made with a thick layer of 14K gold that is pressure-bonded to 
            an underlying core of jeweller's brass. Unlike plated metals, the outer layer of gold 
            filled jewelry will not flake off. It offers the quality and longevity of solid karat 
            gold pieces, but at a more accessible price. It's also nickel-free and hypoallergenic, 
            which makes it perfect for anybody with sensitive skin!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="container">
        <div class="label">
          <p>How should I care for my jewelry?</p>
		</div>
        <hr>
        <div class="content">
          <p>Most of our jewelry requires a minimal care routine. Read our 
            <a href="https://abbey-park-dev-store.myshopify.com/pages/care-guide">care instructions</a>
